---
title: Ginger-Soy Chicken & Veggie Stir-Fry with Pickled Cucumber & Garlic Rice
description: Is it time to lift your stir-fry game? Here's a delicious lesson in how to get ginger-marinated chicken, tender veggies and a
flavour-packed sauce. With a few simple tricks – cooking the meat in batches, getting the veggies started before adding the sauce
and adding flavour to the rice with garlic – you'll be a stir-fry superstar in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652f8b0a19da7d8129dcef9d-53a4ccf4.jpeg
